      <title>美元普遍走强拖累印度卢比跌至历史低点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-20/indian-rupee-hits-record-low-as-broad-dollar-strength-weighs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于美元普遍走强令多数亚洲新兴货币承压，印度卢比跌至历史最低点。]]></description>
